Sphere: Summoning Sphere<br/>
<br/>
<br/>
Usage cast tsunami<br/>
<br/>
When cast, this spell will cause immense masses of water to tip any boat near<br/>
the druid who summoned the tsunami.  This will aid the caster in battle by<br/>
throwing the enemy overboard.  For the spell to work you must be sailing or<br/>
swimming this powerful spell summons a tidal wave before the caster which<br/>
washes all people and small objects away. <br/><br/>
